Ass kamel ttqahhiren-iyi yeɛdawen-iw.
D acu i yezmer a yi-t-ixdem wemdan?.
taqbaylit ttutlayt-iw, s-yes ad zuxxeɣ
aɛenni ɣer Yillu.
ufiɣ iman-iw.
kunwi tellufḍa-m.
D icewwiqen n ṛṛuḥ.
anwa iyellan d anezmar am kečč ay Ameɣlal.
Ayagi ad aɣ-yawi iwakken ad ǧǧuǧgent deg-nneɣ tissas.
Tira iqedsen.
iɛerqasen ced uyeddid.
anezgum d ixemmimen.
D ayen ɣer ssaramen imezwura.
teǧam-iyi ger ibardan.
awid afus-ik
d lehna neɣ d ṭrad.
D tiswiɛin deg ttidiren
